abstract: "A Google Earth Engine implementation combining five cloud detection methods (SCL, s2cloudless, Cloud Score+ cs, Cloud Score+ cs_cdf, and shadow projection) using pixel-union logic with confidence scoring. Optimized for water quality remote sensing applications."
